song_lyrics: Muni man manjan Shrī Ghanshyām dharmakul ranjan... °ṭek
Karī ke prakāsh gyān māyā tam kiyo nāsa,
Karī kop kiratār asurako kiyo sanhāra,
Mathyo mān krodh kām lobh moh ganjana... Muni° 2
